			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Speak to the merregon after peacefully resolving SHA_Orthon_TrespassLair\r\n\r\nSteps:\r\n1. Use roll amazing in debug\r\n2. goto -676; -754 in Shar Temple\r\n3. enter the room nearby, walk towards the piles of dead bodies\r\n4. cinematic starts. Pick 1 -> 1 -> 1 -> 1 -> 1 -> 1 -> 2\r\n5. wait for the troops to get into position\r\n6. use teleport S_SHA_Merregon_002 in debug"
				},
